    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS timing. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been performed, including rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension geometry remains true, with updated bushings and dampers providing excellent damping characteristics. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains tight, exhibiting strong compression and a linear power band all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline. An ideal candidate for the purist seeking a robust, performance-oriented chassis.",
