      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, and every button and dial functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound\u2014the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the service records show a history of preventative care, including a recent brake service and fluid flush. While it isn't a showroom trailer queen, it is a dependable, attractive, and high-performing machine that has many miles of adventure left to offer. It has been garage-kept and treated with the respect a fine automobile deserves, making it a fantastic value for its next owner.",
